  "name": "RPlog_Stiff_Convoy_Defense",
  "title": "Raptor and Wildman Against the Convoy",
  "summary": "New Republic pilots Raxis 'Raptor' L'ygr and Lance 'Wildman' lead a Ghost Squadron raid on an Imperial border convoy of two bulk freighters, escorted by A-wings and Y-wings, only to find the Imperials waiting for them. Commodore Krieg launches his TIE squadron immediately as the convoy executes its escape plan, and the dogfight splits into running duels: Raxis tangles with the vengeful Liza Molokai, who is determined to repay him for wounding her in a prior fight, while Lance and Krieg trade daring head-on passes. The fighter screen takes heavy losses on both sides as one freighter is disabled but the second escapes to lightspeed. In the end Liza cripples Raxis's X-Wing and Krieg knocks Lance's ship adrift, leaving both Ghost pilots wounded and helpless as Imperial tractor beams reel them in. Krieg orders his forces to slag the remaining enemy craft and withdraw to the rendezvous, the convoy mission a costly partial Imperial success.",
